creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems of Experience by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; Lois Beachy Yoder; William Lett; Newgatenovelist; Michele Fry; Tina Renee D'Souza; Melissa Hoffman; Larry Wilson; Martha Wilson; Kathleen Moore; Dejan Budimir; Leena Emsley; Matthew Smith; Diana Schmidt; Availle; Kristin Gjerløw
This is another volume of Ella Wheeler Wicox's famous series. This time, the topic is Experience. The short play The New Hawaiian Girl is included in this volume.
The cast of The New Hawaiian Girl is
Narrator: Availle
Ralph: Kristin Gjerløw
Ethel: Diana Schmidt
The Girl: Michele Fry
- Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
